Design a modern mobile fintech application for managing EMIs and recurring subscriptions.

Core features:
- Dashboard showing monthly outgoing total, budget utilization progress bar, and upcoming dues
- EMI tracker with total outstanding debt, active loans count, monthly EMI summary
- Loan cards with progress percentage, paid amount, remaining amount, interest rate, due date, next EMI
- Bills & recharges screen with categories (Mobile, DTH, Electricity, Gas, Internet, Water, Insurance)
- History screen with transaction status (success / failed), timestamps, and amounts
- Add new EMI / subscription flow with form fields: provider name, amount, billing cycle, start date, end date, reminder toggle, notes
- Reminder system UI for upcoming payments and validity expiration

Visual style:
- Clean iOS-style layout
- Soft shadows, rounded cards (16–24px radius)
- Minimalist spacing system (8pt grid)
- Blue primary accent with light gray background
- Subtle gradients on main summary cards
- Professional fintech typography (SF Pro / Inter style)
- Small colorful category icons
- Status pills (success green, failed red)
- Floating action button for adding EMI/subscription

UX principles:
- Information hierarchy: Summary → Details → Actions
- Card-based architecture
- Bottom tab navigation (Home, EMI Tracker, Pay, History, Profile)
- Search bars and filter chips
- Realistic financial data
- Micro-interactions and subtle animations

Produce:
- Multiple iPhone screens in a single presentation:
  1. Home dashboard
  2. EMI tracker
  3. Bills & recharges
  4. History
  5. Add EMI modal

Style references:
Apple Wallet + Paytm + Revolut

High fidelity product UI, realistic production-ready mobile design, soft lighting, clean shadows, professional fintech aesthetic, 4k quality, Figma-style mockups, flat perspective, centered on light neutral background.
